{{#section "plaintext-body"}}
Hi {{{_person.firstName}}}, 

This is a reminder that {{{inviterFirstName}}} {{{inviterLastName}}} has invited you 
to their smart home. Once you accept, you'll have access to the Arcus-connected 
products in {{{_owner.firstName}}}'s place.

To accept your invitation: 
1. Click here to download the Arcus mobile app. 
2. Enter the following invitation code on the initial screen: {{{inviteCode}}}
3. Follow the on-screen instructions. 

By accepting this invitation, you will have limited access to view and/or manage certain aspects of {{{inviterFirstName}}}'s Arcus system.

We recommend contacting {{{inviterFirstName}}} to discuss what action you should take in the event an alarm is triggered.  

If you do not wish to participate, please contact {{{inviterFirstName}}} {{{inviterLastName}}}.

{{/section}}

